	<p>
		<span class="forum_locheader">QD: Club Policies</span><br />
		<a href="index.php">MyAnimeList.net Forum</a>  &raquo;&raquo; <a href="?action=recent&rcp=1">Club Discussion</a> &raquo;&raquo; <a href="/clubs.php?cid=40791"><img src="http://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/info_mylist_tiny.gif" border="0" title="Club Information"></a> <a href="?clubid=40791">Quiet Discourse</a> &raquo;&raquo; <a href="?topicid=708147">QD: Club Policies</a>
	</p><div style="height: 15px; margin: 5px 0px; padding: 3px 0;" class="borderClass">
<div style="float: left;">Must be a Club Member to Reply</div>
